replies.body:
I'm glad Solo/Duo is back but in the same breath why not make it Solo/Duo/Trio, it kind of keeps the dynamic queue playing with more then one friend and also keeps the competitive aspect of the old system. I think that would be a nice compromise. It would kill the "flex queue" you guys have come up with but at the same time you can make that back into ranked 5 Queue which you have specified you are prepared to do. 

Also doing this could allow you guys to make challenger a duo system again which i think most challenger players would enjoy  because if you got to challenger with a friend and then you cant climb further with them you most likely make smurfs and start again rather then trying to climb the top of the ladder and making that more competitive, which is another complaint that keeps coming up.
